database. Specify the SQL database type in the C<type> field and
include the corresponding field. For more information, see Build a
knowledge base by connecting to a structured data source
(https://docs.aws.amazon.com/bedrock/latest/userguide/knowledge-base-build-structured.html)
in the Amazon Bedrock User Guide.

